===Etymology===
{{PIE root|en|bʰuH}}
From {{etyl|fro|en}} {{m|fro|futur}}, from {{etyl|la|en}} {{m|la|futūrus}}, irregular future active participle of {{m|la|sum||I am}}, from {{etyl|ine-pro|en}} {{m|ine-pro|*bʰuH-||to become, be}}. Cognate with {{etyl|ang|-}} {{m|ang|bēo||I become, I will be, I am}}. More at {{l|en|be}}. Displaced native {{etyl|ang|-}} {{m|ang|toweard}} in the given sense.

